# Frontend build-time variables (Vite). These are PUBLIC (compiled into the browser
# bundle) — never put secrets here. Copy to `.env.local` (gitignored) and fill in.

# Google OAuth 2.0 Web client ID for the "Gmail Draft" button (browser-side GIS flow).
# Looks like: 1234567890-abc123.apps.googleusercontent.com
# Setup steps: see GMAIL_DRAFT_SETUP.md
VITE_GMAIL_CLIENT_ID=
